<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>About Coupa</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#f7fafc;
      --card:#ffffff;
      --accent:#0f172a;
      --muted:#6b7280;
      --primary:#2563eb;
    }

    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f8fafc 0%, #eef2f7 100%);
      color:var(--accent);
      min-height:100vh;
      display:flex;
      align-items:flex-start;
      justify-content:center;
      padding:48px 16px;
    }

    .container{
      max-width:900px;
      width:100%;
      background:var(--card);
      border-radius:12px;
      box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(12,18,30,0.08);
      padding:40px;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    /* Top-right button */
    .top-action {
      position: absolute;
      top:16px;
      right:16px;
      display:inline-flex;
      gap:8px;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .btn {
      background:var(--primary);
      color:#fff;
      border:0;
      padding:10px 14px;
      border-radius:8px;
      font-weight:600;
      cursor:pointer;
      text-decoration:none;
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:8px;
      box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(37,99,235,0.18);
    }
    .btn.secondary {
      background:transparent;
      color:var(--accent);
      border:1px solid #e6eefc;
      box-shadow:none;
      font-weight:600;
    }

    header h1{
      margin:0 0 8px 0;
      font-size:1.6rem;
      letter-spacing:-0.01em;
    }

    header p.lead{
      margin:0 0 20px 0;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .content {
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
      gap:28px;
    }

    .card {
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#fff,#fbfdff);
      border-radius:10px;
      padding:18px;
      box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(12,18,30,0.04);
      border:1px solid #f1f7ff;
    }

    .features li { margin-bottom:10px; color:var(--muted); }

    @media (max-width:840px){
      .content{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .top-action { position: static; margin-bottom:16px; }
      .container{ padding:24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="container" role="main" aria-labelledby="page-title">
    <div class="top-action" aria-hidden="false">
      <!-- Top-right button — change href or add onclick as needed -->
      <a class="btn" href="/logout">Log out</a>
    </div>

    <header>
      <h1 id="page-title">About Coupa</h1>
      <p class="lead">Coupa is a cloud-based spend management platform that helps organizations control costs, streamline procurement, and get visibility into company-wide spending.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="content" aria-label="About Coupa details">
      <article>
        <div class="card">
          <h2>What Coupa does</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5rem;">
            Coupa provides software for procurement, invoicing, expense management, and supplier collaboration.
            It centralizes purchasing workflows so companies can enforce policies, reduce maverick spend, and drive cost savings across their organization.
          </p>

          <h3 style="margin-top:14px;">Key benefits</h3>
          <ul class="features" style="padding-left:1.15rem;">
            <li>Visibility into spend and supplier performance</li>
            <li>Automated procurement & approvals</li>
            <li>Better policy compliance and cost control</li>
            <li>Supplier and invoice automation</li>
          </ul>

          <p style="margin-top:14px;color:var(--muted);">This page is a quick summary — link to product pages or your internal documentation for deeper details.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:18px;">
          <a class="btn" href="https://www.coupa.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Coupa.com</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <aside class="card" aria-label="Quick facts">
        <h3>Quick facts</h3>
        <dl style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;">
          <dt style="font-weight:700;">Category</dt><dd>Cloud spend management</dd>
          <dt style="font-weight:700;">Use cases</dt><dd>Procurement, Invoicing, Expense, Supplier Management</dd>
          <dt style="font-weight:700;">Best for</dt><dd>Companies looking to centralize spend and improve compliance</dd>
        </dl>
      </aside>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
